!! Theme and plugin installation

Drag the following tiddlers into your wiki to import them:

* $:/plugins/nico/notebook-mobile
* $:/themes/nico/notebook

!! Setup

* Set the theme to `Notebook`
* Set the colour palette to either `Notebook grey` or `Notebook beige`, or alternatively, click the {{$:/themes/nico/notebook/ui/Buttons/SwitchPalette}} button.